Package: indicator-sound-switcher
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python:Depends},
 python-gi,
 gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1,
 libpulse0
Description: Sound input/output selector indicator
 A simple yet usable application indicator for Ubuntu/Unity. It allows for
 easy switching of the default sound input ("source" in PulseAudio terms) and
 output ("sink") with just a couple of clicks.

